snippet.title: Roger Anderton
snippet.description: Alternative Science/physics; especially dissent against Einstein's relativity. Although relativity is ok, Einstein messed it up, and people working on relativity before Einstein (that nowadays mostly get ignored) had relativity in better shape than what Einstein left it. Modern physics has been built upon mistakes from Einstein, with an Establishment that has tried to enforce those mistakes as dogma; blocking as much as possible any open debate with those dissenting against Einstein.
